{
  "description": "A nighttime view of a city skyline illuminated with city lights and a vibrant fireworks display. A long bridge, likely the Bay Bridge, stretches across dark water in the foreground, its lights creating a prominent linear element. The city behind the bridge is densely packed with skyscrapers, lit up with a multitude of windows. Above the cityscape, fireworks explode in a burst of red, white, and blue, creating a spectacular visual contrast against the dark sky. The overall scene evokes a celebratory and festive atmosphere.  The lower portion of the image is mostly dark water.",
